{
  "stem": "26983.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It had a different--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Locomotive.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But anyhow, the voice was horrifying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we arrived at night in a place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I looked through.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I could see a lot of reflectors, against--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--at night, and some huge balloons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know what it is.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later on, I knew that these hu-- like a very fat fishes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they were antiaircraft balloons which were always put up, because nearby was Buna and some factories, and they were against--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we arrived in main Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know it at the time, but it was--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, suddenly, I saw through when-- still it was terribly quiet, terribly quiet, like death.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I saw many, many people from far in dressed as soldiers or something like that-- military dress.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everyone had a stick in his hand.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I said, well, it must be a recreation home for soldiers or something like that because everyone had a stick in his hand.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I saw only, only these soldiers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But few minutes later, the wagon was opened, and the unhuman crying and shouting, and people with kind of dress I've never seen-- these strips, and with numbers sewn, and all kinds of signs, and screaming like-- not like human beings.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Raus!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Raus!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Leave everything.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Nothing you can take in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Off, off!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Go, go, go,!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Quick, quick, quick!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah,  these people with the stripes, and nearby SS man who encouraged-- los, los, go on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were some huge they called it, DKW, Deutsche Kraft Wagen-- these huge military--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--trucks.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were squeezed in the trucks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But so squeezed that I was afraid I will fell over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was just on, on the border.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The end of it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was worse than sardines.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
